SECTION  SUMMARY
  Techno Functional Workday Consultant with 4+ years of experience in HCM, Payroll, Compensation,
  Integrations, and Benefits, with expertise in Workday Studio, Core Connectors, EIB, and Advanced Report
  Writing.
  Expertise in Workday Extend, Workday Orchestrations, and Custom Object Development, delivering
  tailored solutions to enhance HR, Payroll, and Finance processes.
  Proficient in Python and SQL for data manipulation, integration validation, and creating custom automation
  solutions for HR and payroll workflows.
  Functional experience in Workday HCM, including Employee Lifecycle Management, Compensation
  Planning, and Benefits Administration.
  Managed employee lifecycle processes, including onboarding, offboarding, and employee data management
  within the Workday HRM system.
  Experienced in Workday inbound/outbound integrations, Core Connectors, and Document Transformations.
  Developed Workday Extend applications and Workday Orchestrations to automate complex workflows,
  reducing manual interventions by 30%.
  Proficient in developing and managing inbound/outbound integrations using Studio, Document
  Transformation, and REST APIs for seamless data synchronization with third-party systems such as ADP,
  Kronos, and Fidelity.
  Designed and implemented custom Workday HRIS reports and dashboards to track key HR metrics such as
  turnover rate, employee demographics, and performance management.
  Proficient in the transformation of XML into XSLT and XML into JSON for presenting data for different web
  services.
  Design and develop BIRT Reports as per client s requirement and work on fixing bugs.
  Experienced in creating reusable templates, integration documentation, and migration plans for efficient system
  transitions and knowledge transfer.
  Adept at troubleshooting complex integration issues, performing root cause analysis, and implementing
  scalable solutions that enhance system performance.
  Collaborated with cross-functional teams using Agile methodologies, ensuring timely delivery of solutions and
  fostering efficient communication between technical and business stakeholders.
END_SECTION  SUMMARY

